nt</a></td></tr></table><p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(240,235,224,0.4);line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 8px;">This link expires in <strong style="color:rgba(240,235,224,0.6);">24 hours</strong>. If you did not request this, ignore this email.</p><div style="border-top:1px solid rgba(0,210,255,0.1);margin:32px 0;"></div><p style="font-size:11px;font-family:monospace;letter-spacing:0.25em;color:rgba(0,210,255,0.5);text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px;">// what_you_can_do</p><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"><tr><td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:rgba(240,235,224,0.65);"><span style="color:#00d2ff;margin-right:10px;">◆</span>Automatic bookmark — resume where you left off</td></tr><tr><td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:rgba(240,235,224,0.65);"><span style="color:#00d2ff;margin-right:10px;">◆</span>Vote to recover books from the Lost Writings Bin</td></tr><tr><td style="padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:rgba(240,235,224,0.65);"><span style="color:#00d2ff;margin-right:10px;">◆</span>Leave reviews and comments in the community</td></tr></table><div style="border-top:1px solid rgba(0,210,255,0.1);margin:32px 0;"></div><p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(240,235,224,0.35);line-height:1.7;margin:0;">To delete your account write to <a href="mailto:noreply@liberiamo2076.com" style="color:rgba(0,210,255,0.5);text-decoration:none;">noreply@liberiamo2076.com</a>.</p></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:24px 40px;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,210,255,0.1);text-align:center;"><p style="font-family:monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:rgba(240,235,224,0.25);text-transform:uppercase;margin:0;">© 2076 Liberiamo la mente · liberiamo2076.com</p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>'
) ON CONFLICT (tipo, lingua) DO UPDATE SET oggetto = EXCLUDED.oggetto, corpo_html = EXCLUDED.corpo_html;

INSERT INTO email_templates (tipo, lingua, oggetto, corpo_html) VALUES (
